<Cap><string_1> <equal> <Cap><string_2> + <Cap><string_3> + <Cap><string_4>
<se_def>*: Travellers, are you? Sorry, but I'm under orders not to let anyone through.
<se_def>*: You'll have to turn back.
<se_def>*: There's been a fire in Farebury. They think it might be arson.<page>*: So I'm under orders to keep the gate closed to prevent the culprit escaping.
<se_high>*: Tweety tweety tweet!
<se_def>*: Woof woof WOOF!
<se_high>*: Chirpy chirpy cheep!
<se_def>*: Ruff ruff RUFF!
The horse is gazing out across the wilderness.
<se_low>*: You can get hold of some really good rock salt down there, you know.
<se_low>*: I've been digging it out and selling it to earn a living.
<se_low>*: What's a thing like that doing in the middle of nowhere...?
<se_low>*: Ah! <IF_SOLO>A traveller<ELSE_NOT_SOLO>Travellers<ENDIF_SOLO>! Have you seen that strange-looking mountain over there?
<se_low>*: Look! If you squint a bit, you'll see it. It's a huge mountain shaped just like a ship.
<se_low>*: There's no way there'd be a ship all the way out here, though... It really is a puzzle!
<se_low>*: That mountain over there looks so much like a ship. I'm intrigued!
<se_low>*: If I didn't have to work, I'd go over and take a closer look.
<se_high>*: Coo coo COOOO!
<se_def>*: (Whimper whimper whine!)
The horse is pawing at the grass with its hoof.
<se_low>*: It's about time we set off to peddle our wares, but my partner doesn't seem to want to leave.
<se_low>*: What a pain!
<se_low>*: There was a strange-looking mountain over there before! Where's it gone!?
<se_low>*: There's no way a huge thing like that could just disappear. This is really strange!
<se_high>*: Caw caw CAW!
<se_def>*: Grrr grrr GRRRRR!
<se_low>*: There was this really strange light in the sky to the northwest a while back.
<se_low>*: And an earthquake too. This path was buried under all the rubble.
<se_low>*: Trodain Castle's off in that direction. I wonder what happened there.
<se_def>*: No way through, eh? There be no point tryin' to carry on unless you be in a BIG hurry, arrrr!
<se_def>*: Nothin' worth seein' up there anyway.
The horse is watching its surroundings nervously.
<se_low>*: Ever since the sky turned red, there have been monsters all over the place.
<se_low>*: And staying at the inn for so long left me stony broke.
<se_low>*: I suppose I'll just have to carry on flapping about here!
<se_low>*: I wonder what happened to that strange-looking mountain.
<se_def>*: Bow wow WOW!
<se_def>*: Rrrr ruff ruff!
